org.funcito.functorbase

Class AbstractFunctorBase<T,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.funcito.functorbase.AbstractFunctorBase<T,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The target (input) type of the functor
    V - The output type of the functor
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FunctorBase<T,V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicFunctor, SafeNavFunctor

    public abstract class AbstractFunctorBase<T,V>
extends Object
implements FunctorBase<T,V>
    An abstract partial implementation of the FunctorBase interface, with internal state useful for optimizing executing a single non-chained method call. It is used as the base for all of Funcito's provided basic functor implementations.
